featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Masha allah
A wonderful new mosque has been built in Chamraja Naggar. Ismaily Mohalla main near Rahmath Mohalla. The name of the main mosque is from the name of a big tree which is situated in Barabanki.
New Alhe Sunnat Wa Jamat Masjid In Chamraja Nagar
And there is a lot of peace in the mosque.
Allah gave us the gift of teaching everyone.
Aur hamsa sab milke masjid main zyada se zyada ana hai

And there is a Madrasa here, Subhan Allah
